'''Mining Slaves''' are human slaves found at the [[Desert Mining Camp]] south of the [[Shantay Pass]] in the [[Kharidian desert]] where players must go for the quest [[Tourist Trap]]. They are similar to [[Mining Slave]]s, and get harassed by [[Rowdy Guard]]s at the camp.

